<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{kitto}}}} indicates a high degree of certainty. It can be used with @HI{{deshou}}.
</p>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{tabunn}}}} implies less certainty than when @EM{{@HI{{kitto}}}} is used. It is most often
used with @HI{{deshou}}.
</p>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{moshikashitara}}}} is most often used with @HI{{kamo shiremasenn}}. Of the threee adverbs described here,
this one involves the least amount of certainty.
</p>

